Reviews.Title: QUALITY AND PRICE = HAPPY CUSTOMER .
Reviews.Author: DEMETRI "BOUZOUKI"
Reviews.Content: Excellent product. I have been using Siamese cable on many installations for better signal quality.This product did exactly that, and a very good price.

Reviews.Title: Fantastic Long Distance Cable
Reviews.Author: Clark
Reviews.Content: These cords are great! They were exactly as described and pictured. I had to bend in around dozens of corners while installing around my house, and the video quality was still perfect! I honestly didn't expect how clear it was, since previous cables always gave me low quality video. The electrical power through the attached AWG cord is also very stable. This product exceeded my expectations. These cables are very cheap, absolutely worth the money I spent. This product is a must own.

Reviews.Title: worked
Reviews.Author: Tod Morrow
Reviews.Content: it was what i expected and worked just fine. we hooked up a bunch of cameras in a large facility

Reviews.Title: Good Value
Reviews.Author: J. Fasceski "lcpljoe"
Reviews.Content: Delivered as promised and as described. Would recommend for long wire runs and larger installations. The word requirement for a review is excessive. I refuse to do any more.
